                     <interp inst="t18340703-35-person298" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am in the prosecutor's service. I saw the prisoner - I heard a snap, and saw the table-cloth coming down - the prisoner wrapped it up, and put it under her shawl - my mistress came round, and the prisoner said she was going to give it to me, but it was concealed under her shawl - she had been going out, but she went back when she saw me - it could not have come down, and I heard it snap.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was coming out, and the wind blew it in my face. I did not conceal it.</p>
